Title: Gathering Intel
Text: Ms. Sophia Rodriguez, a resident who was recently assaulted in the park, awaits my assistance. I need to gather more information about the assailant to aid in the investigation. She can be found in Serenity Court, the tranquil courtyard in the Downtown district.
CompleteText: I've spoken with Ms. Sophia Rodriguez and obtained details about the assault. Now, armed with this information, I must set out to identify the assailant and ensure justice is served.
